10:T4d8,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Person","name":"Christine Bermas","image":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zdFbplqeZbzgCJEJfnj1pPqVVH2.jpg","description":"Christine Bermas is a Filipino actress and model born on August 30, 2001, in Manila, Philippines. She began her career in entertainment as a member of the girl group Belladonnas before transitioning to acting in 2021. Christine gained recognition for her performances in Vivamax films such as Moonlight Butterfly (2022), Scorpio Nights 3 (2022), Island of Desire (2022), Relyebo (2022), Nightbird (2023), and Lampas Langit (2023).\n\nKnown for portraying daring and mature roles, she has often emphasized the difference between her on-screen persona and her real-life personality, describing herself as conservative off-camera. Before entering show business, she worked humble jobs, including selling local delicacies, to support her family.\n\nChristine continues to build her reputation as one of Vivamax’s most prominent young actresses, with aspirations to take on more dramatic and emotionally challenging roles in Philippine cinema.","jobTitle":"Acting","url":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/people/585941/christine-bermas","sameAs":["https://imdb.com/name/nm12763049"]}5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$10"}}],["$","$L11",null,{"person":{"id":"45b12e90-b857-4ecc-96ad-dd7cf9fe975f","tmdb_id":3371804,"name":"Christine Bermas","gender":1,"biography":"Christine Bermas is a Filipino actress and model born on August 30, 2001, in Manila, Philippines. She began her career in entertainment as a member of the girl group Belladonnas before transitioning to acting in 2021. Christine gained recognition for her performances in Vivamax films such as Moonlight Butterfly (2022), Scorpio Nights 3 (2022), Island of Desire (2022), Relyebo (2022), Nightbird (2023), and Lampas Langit (2023).\n\nKnown for portraying daring and mature roles, she has often emphasized the difference between her on-screen persona and her real-life personality, describing herself as conservative off-camera. Before entering show business, she worked humble jobs, including selling local delicacies, to support her family.\n\nChristine continues to build her reputation as one of Vivamax’s most prominent young actresses, with aspirations to take on more dramatic and emotionally challenging roles in Philippine cinema.","birthday":"2001-08-30","deathday":null,"place_of_birth":"Manila, Philippines ","profile_path":"/zdFbplqeZbzgCJEJfnj1pPqVVH2.jpg","known_for_department":"Acting","popularity":8.9593,"imdb_id":"nm12763049","created_at":"2026-02-25T23:29:06.127714+00:00","updated_at":"2026-02-26T22:43:48.774+00:00","also_known_as":["کریستین برماس"],"homepage":null,"adult":false,"wikipedia_url":null,"bio_source":"tmdb","import_batch_id":null,"import_batch_name":null,"imported_at":"2026-02-25T23:29:06.127714+00:00","main_profile_photo":"/zdFbplqeZbzgCJEJfnj1pPqVVH2.jpg","images":{"tagged":[{"id":"61d7054f497560008f043c10","width":1066,"height":1600,"file_path":"/fgOB02Ll0vlJ1cwcjxUbqcviIdf.jpg","media_type":"movie","vote_average":1.75}],"profiles":[{"width":300,"height":450,"file_path":"/zdFbplqeZbzgCJEJfnj1pPqVVH2.jpg","aspect_ratio":0.667,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-26T22:43:48.774+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"external_ids":null,"social_ids":null,"combined_credits_count":0,"gdvg_id":585941,"native_name":null,"instagram":null,"twitter":null,"tiktok":null,"height_cm":null,"wikidata_id":null}}]]
9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"Christine Bermas | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"Christine Bermas is a Filipino actress and model born on August 30, 2001, in Manila, Philippines. She began her career in entertainment as a member of the girl group Belladonnas before transitioning to acting in 2021. Christine gained recognition for her performances in Vivamax films such as Moonlight Butterfly (2022), Scorpio Nights 3 (2022), Island of Desire (2022), Relyebo (2022), Nightbird (2023), and Lampas Langit (2023).\n\nKnown for portraying daring and mature roles, she has often emphasized the difference between her on-screen persona and her real-life personality, describing herself as conservative off-camera. Before entering show business, she worked humble jobs, including selling local delicacies, to support her family.\n\nChristine continues to build her reputation as one of Vivamax’s most prominent young actresses, with aspirations to take on more dramatic and emotionally challenging roles in Philippine cinema."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/people/585941/christine-bermas"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"Christine Bermas"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"Christine Bermas is a Filipino actress and model born on August 30, 2001, in Manila, Philippines. She began her career in entertainment as a member of the girl group Belladonnas before transitioning to acting in 2021. Christine gained recognition for her performances in Vivamax films such as Moonlight Butterfly (2022), Scorpio Nights 3 (2022), Island of Desire (2022), Relyebo (2022), Nightbird (2023), and Lampas Langit (2023).\n\nKnown for portraying daring and mature roles, she has often emphasized the difference between her on-screen persona and her real-life personality, describing herself as conservative off-camera. Before entering show business, she worked humble jobs, including selling local delicacies, to support her family.\n\nChristine continues to build her reputation as one of Vivamax’s most prominent young actresses, with aspirations to take on more dramatic and emotionally challenging roles in Philippine cinema."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/people/585941/christine-bermas"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/zdFbplqeZbzgCJEJfnj1pPqVVH2.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"profile"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"Christine Bermas"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"Christine Bermas is a Filipino actress and model born on August 30, 2001, in Manila, Philippines. She began her career in entertainment as a member of the girl group Belladonnas before transitioning to acting in 2021. Christine gained recognition for her performances in Vivamax films such as Moonlight Butterfly (2022), Scorpio Nights 3 (2022), Island of Desire (2022), Relyebo (2022), Nightbird (2023), and Lampas Langit (2023).\n\nKnown for portraying daring and mature roles, she has often emphasized the difference between her on-screen persona and her real-life personality, describing herself as conservative off-camera. Before entering show business, she worked humble jobs, including selling local delicacies, to support her family.\n\nChristine continues to build her reputation as one of Vivamax’s most prominent young actresses, with aspirations to take on more dramatic and emotionally challenging roles in Philippine cinema."}],"$L12","$L13","$L14"],"error":null,"digest":"$undefined"}
